{"tid":2115980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《新华社》宣稱蠟染工藝「源自中国」     印尼網友：何不宣稱「新冠病毒來自中国？」","createTime":"2020-07-20T01:09:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T05:04:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"636e842df740fb5135161d0ddd55b88508ea7884","tid":2115980,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:09:43.000Z","msg":"中共官方通訊社《新華社》12日在推特發布影片，介紹「常見於中國少數民族」的傳統工藝&mdash;蠟染，並加上「中國不可思議」的標籤，卻戳痛印尼國家自豪感的敏感神經，因而在社群媒體引發軒然大波，數百名憤慨的印尼網友湧入貼文留言，批評《新華社》將源自印尼的蠟染文化據為己有，甚至扯上中印南海主權爭端，直批：「繼我國海域之後，（中國）現在又要宣稱我們的文化也是中國的嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/article/2866514\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Farticle%2F2866514&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8pkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=6483a140\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/article/2866514</a>"},{"pid":"e3645415c53c08addaf66bec8e3ba302ef208a8c","tid":2115980,"uid":327462,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zuevhnY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzuevhnY.gif&h=1971e62e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c4265baea47e3e4e6a90a465a93263b0c526214","tid":2115980,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:25:47.000Z","msg":"識玩"},{"pid":"8607675faad4ed0a93ea4f16f518fb1693d20ba1","tid":2115980,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}